### -----------------ADMIN-------------------

### Register Admin
POST http://localhost:8080/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Manpreet",
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "1234",
  "role": "ROLE_ADMIN"
}


### ADMIN TOKEN
POST http://localhost:8080/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

### ---------------------------USER-------------------
### REGISTER USER
POST http://localhost:8080/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Manpreet",
  "email": "user@gmail.com",
  "password": "1234",
  "role": "ROLE_USER"
}

### Login (user TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:8080/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@gmail.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

